                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-filled text-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-1 text-2xl">check_circle</span>
                            <div>
                                <p class="font-semibold text-on-surface mb-1">Tüketin</p>
                                <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Omega-3 (somon, sardalya, ceviz), kürkumin, yeşil çay, yeşil yapraklı sebzeler, tam tahıllar, zeytinyağı, mevsim meyveleri.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
